00:33:50.850 --> 00:33:52.277
That what you see on paper

00:33:52.277 --> 00:33:54.130
and what you can mix up in a vile

00:33:54.130 --> 00:33:58.280
is often vastly different
than what you predict.

00:33:58.280 --> 00:33:59.160
- Right.
- Right.

00:33:59.160 --> 00:34:01.710
- And there's a dose effect
curve that's really interesting.

00:34:01.710 --> 00:34:06.420
