00:36:56.030 --> 00:37:00.950
not to be the guy in
the corner of the room,

00:37:00.950 --> 00:37:02.950
where everyone's trying to just
have a good time and relax,

00:37:02.950 --> 00:37:04.600
like crying about your mother.

00:37:04.600 --> 00:37:05.630
Your other friends,

00:37:05.630 --> 00:37:07.110
they're having an experience too,

00:37:07.110 --> 00:37:09.620
and you're being a drama
king, and blah-blah-blah,

00:37:09.620 --> 00:37:11.480
And so, yeah, compose yourself.

00:37:11.480 --> 00:37:12.820
Hold your-
