00:39:55.490 --> 00:39:59.040
pay attention to many things
at once, not just one.

00:39:59.040 --> 00:40:00.630
Is that-
- Especially these days.

00:40:00.630 --> 00:40:01.463
Yeah, multi-task.
- Exactly.

00:40:01.463 --> 00:40:02.296
Yeah.
- Right.

00:40:02.296 --> 00:40:03.129
Multitask.

00:40:03.129 --> 00:40:05.520
And the more that we focus on one thing,

00:40:05.520 --> 00:40:06.730
the more bizarre that thing

00:40:06.730 --> 00:40:08.460
