00:40:15.126 --> 00:40:16.340
weird things.
- Yeah.

00:40:16.340 --> 00:40:17.173
- Right?

00:40:17.173 --> 00:40:19.510
- I think if that as the
classic psychedelic effect,

00:40:19.510 --> 00:40:21.447
or one classic effect,

00:40:21.447 --> 00:40:22.920
and one I've used many times,

00:40:22.920 --> 00:40:27.380
of this example of why
people should necessarily...

00:40:28.340 --> 00:40:29.260
These aren't...

