Like the entire universe
has essentially conspired

00:40:53.540 --> 00:40:55.370
to come to this one point

00:40:55.370 --> 00:40:57.650
to make this absolutely breathtaking...

00:40:57.650 --> 00:41:00.720
It's almost like, I think,
of the simplest form of...

00:41:00.720 --> 00:41:01.553
Well, we know that the

00:41:01.553 --> 00:41:03.070
