00:41:56.030 --> 00:41:57.990
But it sounds like on psychedelics,

00:41:57.990 --> 00:41:59.870
one of the primary goals therapeutically

00:41:59.870 --> 00:42:03.620
is to really drill into one
of these perceptual bubbles,

00:42:03.620 --> 00:42:04.900
and expand that bubble.

00:42:04.900 --> 00:42:06.800
And the safety, it seems,
- Yeah.

00:42:06.800 --> 00:42:08.370
- is the safety...

00:42:08.370 --> 00:42:11.400
It's sort of like a permission to do that

00:42:12.977 --> 00:42:14.180
without worrying that
something's going to happen.

00:42:14.180 --> 00:42:15.013
- Right.

