01:07:11.850 --> 01:07:14.120
- Hallucinogen-persisting
perceptual disorder,

01:07:14.120 --> 01:07:16.090
who have never taken a psychedelic.

01:07:16.090 --> 01:07:21.090
So it's often prompted by
alcohol, benzodiazepines,

01:07:22.480 --> 01:07:25.273
cannabis, even tobacco.

01:07:26.300 --> 01:07:29.500
And I believe, in one individual,

01:07:29.500 --> 01:07:31.210
no lifetime history of any,

01:07:31.210 --> 01:07:35.990
it wasn't proceeded by any
of those substance uses.

01:07:35.990 --> 01:07:37.380
So I think it's...

01:07:38.780 --> 01:07:39.630
