01:07:39.630 --> 01:07:42.700
the precipitation exacerbation
of psychotic disorders.

01:07:42.700 --> 01:07:44.780
It seems pretty clear through observation

01:07:44.780 --> 01:07:47.960
that some people with
either predisposition

01:07:47.960 --> 01:07:49.910
or active psychotic disease,

