The same way that a life experience

01:07:54.350 --> 01:07:55.320
can destabilize this
- Sure.

01:07:55.320 --> 01:07:56.400
- person more easily.

01:07:56.400 --> 01:07:57.233
I think of it like that.

01:07:57.233 --> 01:07:58.110
There's probably some

01:07:58.110 --> 01:08:00.710
pretty rare neurological susceptibility.

01:08:00.710 --> 01:08:03.470
We have tended, this
goes back to the '80s,

01:08:05.040 --> 01:08:07.590
clinical practice, it ended up in the DSM

01:08:07.590 --> 01:08:08.810
focused on hallucinogen,

01:08:08.810 --> 01:08:13.810
because I relate it to the
psychology of xenophobia.

01:08:13.860 --> 01:08:16.820
It's always the weird other
thing that gets the attribution.

