You don't attribute to the thing,

01:08:18.820 --> 01:08:20.650
like, oh yeah. did you smoke cigarettes?

01:08:20.650 --> 01:08:21.483
Did you drink?

01:08:21.483 --> 01:08:22.316
It's like, well, yeah,

01:08:22.316 --> 01:08:23.690
but I see lots of people drinking,

01:08:23.690 --> 01:08:25.650
and not ending up with this.

01:08:25.650 --> 01:08:29.170
You take a crazy drug,

