01:11:28.900 --> 01:11:31.660
And we have no understanding

01:11:31.660 --> 01:11:33.830
of the duration of that process.

01:11:33.830 --> 01:11:37.490
However, the experience of any drug

01:11:37.490 --> 01:11:39.440
or any life experience, right?

01:11:39.440 --> 01:11:42.020
Even if it's a trauma, or
a wonderful experience,

01:11:42.020 --> 01:11:44.410
or a psychedelic experience,
it doesn't matter,

01:11:44.410 --> 01:11:48.010
sets in motion a series
of dominoes that fall,

01:11:48.010 --> 01:11:49.580
and it's the falling of those dominoes

01:11:49.580 --> 01:11:51.030
that we call neuroplasticity.

01:11:51.030 --> 01:11:54.180
I mean, the reshaping of neural
circuits could take years.

01:11:54.180 --> 01:11:55.120
We don't know.

01:11:55.120 --> 01:11:56.450
It's the trigger,

01:11:56.450 --> 01:11:58.120
and then there's the actual change.

01:11:58.120 --> 01:12:00.540
And so I think that some
of what you described

01:12:00.540 --> 01:12:03.790
