02:02:55.300 --> 02:02:56.470
and things of that sort.

02:02:56.470 --> 02:02:58.670
So some of it may relate to that.

02:02:58.670 --> 02:02:59.503
But I have to say,

02:02:59.503 --> 02:03:03.270
that even prior to all
that academic pressure,

02:03:03.270 --> 02:03:04.960
when I went there,

02:03:04.960 --> 02:03:06.930
the pressure wasn't like that.

02:03:06.930 --> 02:03:11.930
We had an unusual number of
suicides for whatever reason,

02:03:13.372 --> 02:03:17.230
and so the idea of kids being prescribed,

02:03:17.230 --> 02:03:18.720
and I want to emphasize prescribed,

02:03:18.720 --> 02:03:19.553
not just using,

02:03:19.553 --> 02:03:22.150
but prescribed psychedelics
for therapeutic purposes,

02:03:22.150 --> 02:03:24.600
I think might make some people balk,

02:03:24.600 --> 02:03:29.500
but the idea of kids killing themselves

02:03:29.500 --> 02:03:30.820
should also make people balk.

02:03:30.820 --> 02:03:34.220
And so I'm relieved to hear
that there's going to be

02:03:34.220 --> 02:03:36.630
a rational, scientific,

02:03:36.630 --> 02:03:40.063
safe clinical trial-based
exploration of this.

02:03:41.920 --> 02:03:45.420
I want to ask you about the current status

02:03:45.420 --> 02:03:47.131
