02:04:52.160 --> 02:04:56.810
companies focused on
psychedelics as therapeutics,

02:04:56.810 --> 02:04:58.823
or psychedelics generally.

02:04:58.823 --> 02:05:01.090
I have to assume that they are investing

02:05:01.090 --> 02:05:04.143
in anticipation of a
shift in the legal status.

02:05:05.570 --> 02:05:07.670
And there's a lot of interest now,

02:05:07.670 --> 02:05:11.530
like will psilocybin
become a taxable thing,

02:05:11.530 --> 02:05:12.430
just like marijuana?

02:05:12.430 --> 02:05:14.400
So let's start with the question of like,

02:05:14.400 --> 02:05:18.110
what is going on in the US legally?

02:05:18.110 --> 02:05:23.110
Is it illegal to possess, and
sell, and use these compounds?

02:05:24.480 --> 02:05:26.550
My understanding is,
you can still go to jail

02:05:26.550 --> 02:05:30.300
for having these compounds
in your possession,

02:05:30.300 --> 02:05:31.530
or for selling.
- Right.

02:05:31.530 --> 02:05:35.610
So even though the legal landscape

02:05:35.610 --> 02:05:38.310
is very different than with cannabis,

02:05:38.310 --> 02:05:39.730
there are some similarities.

02:05:39.730 --> 02:05:41.250
So one of the similarities is,

02:05:41.250 --> 02:05:44.720
that regardless of what local, municipal,

02:05:44.720 --> 02:05:47.450
whether the city or
state is decriminalized,

02:05:47.450 --> 02:05:51.410
and that word itself can mean many things.

