02:06:05.100 --> 02:06:05.933
- Turn the other cheek

02:06:05.933 --> 02:06:06.810
kind of thing.
- Right.

02:06:06.810 --> 02:06:08.080
But even the cops can

02:06:08.080 --> 02:06:10.690
still choose to-
- But someone could get

02:06:10.690 --> 02:06:12.300
pulled over for one thing, searched,

