and then by definition, if
it's illegal, and they find it,

02:06:15.360 --> 02:06:16.440
- Right.
- then they have-

02:06:16.440 --> 02:06:17.406
- So those are-
- They have to do

02:06:17.406 --> 02:06:18.239
something about it.

02:06:18.239 --> 02:06:21.020
- And that'll probably be determined by

02:06:21.020 --> 02:06:22.500
both judicial precedent,

02:06:22.500 --> 02:06:23.790
is it going to be thrown out,

02:06:23.790 --> 02:06:25.950
and just the local prosecutor,

02:06:25.950 --> 02:06:27.570
even before, are they going to choose,

02:06:27.570 --> 02:06:28.600
even at post-arrest,

02:06:28.600 --> 02:06:31.980
are going to pursue to really
go after those charges,

02:06:31.980 --> 02:06:33.750
make those charges stick?

02:06:33.750 --> 02:06:34.950
So I think that's still in play,

02:06:34.950 --> 02:06:36.450
and is going to depend
on the municipality.

02:06:36.450 --> 02:06:38.410
But like cannabis,

