federally, these are all
Schedule I compounds.

02:06:40.640 --> 02:06:42.030
- Which means they're illegal?

02:06:42.030 --> 02:06:43.910
- Which means they're illegal.

02:06:43.910 --> 02:06:44.900
The caveat to that,

02:06:44.900 --> 02:06:46.180
just has always been the case

02:06:46.180 --> 02:06:49.400
since Prop 215 in California
with cannabis in '96,

