is done at the local and state level.

02:06:55.760 --> 02:06:59.630
The DEA, which is the federal
level of law enforcement,

02:06:59.630 --> 02:07:02.190
is a tiny fraction of the arrests.

02:07:02.190 --> 02:07:04.900
I mean, most people that
are arrested for any drug

02:07:04.900 --> 02:07:09.900
are done by local or
state level authorities,

02:07:10.390 --> 02:07:13.230
but it's still technically illegal.

02:07:13.230 --> 02:07:14.190
And so you can,

02:07:14.190 --> 02:07:16.100
and they could potentially,

02:07:16.100 --> 02:07:18.450
depending on the ambiguity
of the local law,

02:07:18.450 --> 02:07:20.160
even those local
officials could charge you

02:07:20.160 --> 02:07:21.853
with a federal crime.

02:07:22.853 --> 02:07:27.160
And theoretically, the
feds could always come in.

02:07:27.160 --> 02:07:29.330
Now, although you'll...

02:07:29.330 --> 02:07:32.973
Again, a similar case with
the whole cannabis history.

